{"tid":800652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國放寬南韓、巴西、阿根廷鋼鋁配額限制","createTime":"2018-08-31T04:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T10:58:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc00f27ce65e449396cb3ad1485f50253bdf62e","tid":800652,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T04:59:53.000Z","msg":"美國放寬南韓、巴西、阿根廷鋼鋁配額限制<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2150080/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E3%80%81%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E3%80%81%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E9%8B%BC%E9%8B%81%E9%85%8D%E9%A1%8D%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2150080%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E3%2580%2581%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E3%2580%2581%25E9%2598%25BF%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E9%258B%25BC%25E9%258B%2581%25E9%2585%258D%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6&d=2w%2Bf58oZeIvkdAHGcO9PKzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=306ac4c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2150080/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E3%80%81%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E3%80%81%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E9%8B%BC%E9%8B%81%E9%85%8D%E9%A1%8D%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部表示，總統特朗普已簽署公告，向南韓、巴西及阿根廷三國，放寬入口鋼鐵和鋁材配額限制。加拿大、墨西哥本周有望與美國完成《北美自由貿易協定》（NAFTA）重新談判，卻未在放寬鋼鋁配額受惠國家之列。<br />\n<br />\n華府宣佈放寬南韓、巴西及阿根廷鋼鐵，以及阿根廷鋁材配額限制。公告表示，企業需要的鋼鐵和鋁材種類，如因美國產能不足或質量未達標而需要入口，則可申請豁免佔用配額，毋須繳付關稅。<br />\n<br />\n美國早前向進口鋼鐵和鋁材加徵關稅，並實施配額制度。美方限定進口南韓及巴西鋼鐵數量，為2015至2017年平均數量70%。"},{"pid":"8c47cddfdac241cced3d7b5fedd624cf8f281fc5","tid":800652,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71e9d4969db122f44347f967b1a1151e5019c26","tid":800652,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"}]}